INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2015-09-29 07:36:32','2015-09-29 07:36:32','Chào mừng đến với <a href=\"http://greenhub.khoahocwordpress.net/\">Multisite environment Trang Mạng</a>. Đây là bài viết đầu tiên của bạn. Bạn có thể chỉnh sửa hoặc xóa bài này, và bắt đầu blog!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2015-09-29 07:36:32','2015-09-29 07:36:32','',0,'http://greenhub.khoahocwordpress.net/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(3,1,'2015-09-29 07:36:45','2015-09-29 07:36:45','','Trang chu','','publish','open','open','','trang-chu','','','2015-09-29 07:36:45','2015-09-29 07:36:45','',0,'http://greenhub.khoahocwordpress.net/trang-chu/',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2015-09-29 07:36:55','2015-09-29 07:36:55','','Lien he','','publish','open','open','','lien-he','','','2015-09-29 07:36:55','2015-09-29 07:36:55','',0,'http://greenhub.khoahocwordpress.net/lien-he/',0,'page','',0),(5,1,'2015-09-29 07:36:58','2015-09-29 07:36:58','A virtual office is the most brilliant solution for businesses that desires the benefits of a physical office but not the space. Having a virtual office means that they can obtain a business address and a full-time receptionist to answer calls and handle mail at a low-cost. In addition, they may have access to hot-desking and meeting rooms on a pay-as-you-go basis. Acquiring a virtual office allows business owners to work anywhere, anytime and yet maintain their professional image. Additional monthly ad-hoc services can be easily setup if required. Another benefit from a virtual office is the smooth transition to a serviced office when the business grows and requires a physical space.','Gioi thieu','','publish','open','open','','gioi-thieu','','','2015-09-29 11:21:42','2015-09-29 11:21:42','',0,'http://greenhub.khoahocwordpress.net/gioi-thieu/',0,'page','',0),(6,1,'2015-09-29 07:37:01','2015-09-29 07:37:01','A virtual office is the most brilliant solution for businesses that desires the benefits of a physical office but not the space. Hav